Package hu.bme.mit.theta.xsts.dsl.gen

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    XstsDslListener
    This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by XstsDslParser.
    XstsDslVisitor<T>
    This interface defines a complete generic visitor for a parse tree produced by XstsDslParser.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    XstsDslBaseListener
    This class provides an empty implementation of XstsDslListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
    XstsDslBaseVisitor<T>
    This class provides an empty implementation of XstsDslVisitor, which can be extended to create a visitor which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
